data.description:
This exquisite mountain residence is on a sprawling 10-acre plot, offering a serene retreat amidst nature's splendor. Home has had several recent updates. The home's design features large windows and vaulted ceilings with skylights, ensuring that each room is bathed in natural light while offering stunning views of the surrounding landscape.
The interior boasts elegant hardwood flooring and a newly updated kitchen, complete with an oversized island, high-end stainless steel appliances, a double oven, and a spacious pantry. The kitchen's granite countertops and a butcher block island with a cooktop are both stylish and functional.
On the second floor, a loft/study area provides a versatile space for work or relaxation. The expansive master bedroom is a true sanctuary, featuring a custom-designed walk-in closet. The adjoining master bathroom is equally luxurious, with a spacious glass shower. Additionally, a second bedroom comes with an ensuite bathroom, adding to the home's convenience and privacy.
The walkout basement opens to an all-season room, complemented by a living area and a modernized bathroom equipped with a steam shower. This level also houses a library/study and ample storage space.
Outside, the deck and the walkout basement lead to where you can enjoy panoramic views of Long Scraggy Peak. The property also includes a detached two-car garage and a canvas carport, offering outdoor storage options.
Residents have the privilege of walking to the National Forest and extensive bike trails. The property also includes access to a fishing pond, adding an element of leisure and exclusivity to this magnificent mountain home. 
Home has full house 22kw Gen and full house water softener and reverse osmosis. There have been a lot of updates and beautiful enhancements to this amazing 10-acre property. Too many upgrades and "nice touches" to list. It's a must-see
